Title: Dune: Part Two
Description: In Dune: Part Two, Paul Atreides' legendary journey continues in the company of Chani and the Fremen as he seeks revenge on those who caused his family's downfall. Paul will have to choose between the love of his life and the fate of the universe to avoid the terrible future he alone has foreseen.

Title: Bob Marley: One Love
Description: One man. One message. One revolution. One legend. Bob Marley: One Love celebrates the life and music of an icon who inspired generations with his message of love and unity. For the first time on the big screen, discover Bob Marley's powerful story of overcoming adversity and the journey behind his revolutionary music.

Title: Imaginary
Description: The new horror film from Blumhouse Productions, the makers of Five Nights at Freddy's and M3GAN. When Jessica moves back to her parents' house, her stepdaughter Alice finds a teddy bear in the basement that she forms a close bond with.

Title: Anyone But You
Description: In the comedy Anyone But You, Bea (Sydney Sweeney) and Ben (Glen Powell) seem like the perfect couple, but after a great first date, something happens that causes their fiery attraction to cool to freezing - until they are unexpectedly paired together at a wedding in Australia. And what do two adults do then? Pretend they're a couple, of course.

Title: Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes
Description: Set years after the events of the previous films, Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes explores the evolving power dynamics between humans and apes. In a rapidly changing world, both species struggle to coexist in an unstable peace. When a new threat emerges, loyalties are tested and leadership is challenged in the fight for survival.

Title: Civil War
Description: In Civil War, ideological differences between Captain America and Iron Man lead to a fractious battle among superheroes. Divided over the government's oversight of their actions, the Avengers must navigate their personal beliefs and the public's safety, leading to a fierce confrontation that tests their bonds and the future of the team.

Title: Ghostbusters: Frozen Empire
Description: Ghostbusters: Frozen Empire takes the legendary ghost hunters to the icy plains of Antarctica where an ancient spectral force is unleashed. The team must use their wits, bravery, and new cryogenic technology to contain this chilling threat before it freezes over the entire world.

Title: Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire
Description: Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire sees the two titans clashing once again, this time against a backdrop of a futuristic cityscape where humanity has reached new technological heights. As a new enemy surfaces, Godzilla and Kong must decide whether to continue their rivalry or join forces against a common threat that could spell extinction for them both.

Title: Tarot
Description: In the mystical thriller Tarot, a young woman gifted in the art of tarot card reading is drawn into a complex web of mystery when she discovers a set of cards with the power to manipulate reality. As she delves deeper, she must use her skills to uncover the truth behind the cards' origins and their dangerous potential before it's too late.
